trans-unit.source: Represents a collection of designers.
trans-unit.target: Representerer en samling av utviklere.

trans-unit.source: This collection object can store references to a set of designers.
trans-unit.target: Dette samlingsobjektet kan inneholde referanser til et sett med utviklere.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerCollection"></xref> class that contains the specified set of designers.
trans-unit.target: Initialiserer en ny forekomst av den <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerCollection"> </xref> klassen som inneholder det angitte settet med utviklere.

trans-unit.source: A list that contains the collection of designers to add.
trans-unit.target: En liste som inneholder samlingen av utviklere å legge til.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerCollection"></xref> class that contains the specified designers.
trans-unit.target: Initialiserer en ny forekomst av den <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerCollection"> </xref> klassen som inneholder de angitte utviklere.

trans-unit.source: Creates a new designer collection from an array of designers.
trans-unit.target: Oppretter en ny designer samling fra en lang rekke utviklere.

trans-unit.source: The collection does not clone the array.
trans-unit.target: Samlingen ikke klone matrisen.

trans-unit.source: An array of <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Design.IDesignerHost"></xref> objects to store.
trans-unit.target: En matrise av <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Design.IDesignerHost"> </xref> objekter til å lagre.

trans-unit.source: Gets the number of designers in the collection.
trans-unit.target: Henter antall utviklere i samlingen.

trans-unit.source: The number of designers in the collection.
trans-unit.target: Antall utviklere i samlingen.

trans-unit.source: Gets a new enumerator for this collection.
trans-unit.target: Henter dataenumerator nye for denne samlingen.

trans-unit.source: An <xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator> that enumerates the collection.
trans-unit.target: En <xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator>som lister opp samlingen.</xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator>

trans-unit.source: Gets the designer at the specified index.
trans-unit.target: Henter designer i den angitte indeksen.

trans-unit.source: The index of the designer to return.
trans-unit.target: Indeksen for utformeren for å returnere.

trans-unit.source: The designer at the specified index.
trans-unit.target: Designer i den angitte indeksen.

trans-unit.source: Copies the elements of the collection to an <xref:System.Array>, starting at a particular <xref:System.Array> index.
trans-unit.target: Overfører av elementene i samlingen til en <xref:System.Array>, med Start fra en bestemt <xref:System.Array>indeksen.</xref:System.Array> </xref:System.Array>

trans-unit.source: The one-dimensional <xref:System.Array> that is the destination of the elements copied from collection.
trans-unit.target: Den endimensjonal <xref:System.Array>som er målet for elementene kopieres fra samlingen.</xref:System.Array>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Array> must have zero-based indexing.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Array>må ha nullbasert indeksering.</xref:System.Array>

trans-unit.source: The zero-based index in `array` at which copying begins.
trans-unit.target: Den nullbaserte indeksen i `array` som kopiering begynner.

trans-unit.source: Gets the number of elements contained in the collection.
trans-unit.target: Henter antallet elementer i samlingen.

trans-unit.source: The number of elements contained in the collection.
trans-unit.target: Antallet elementer i samlingen.

trans-unit.source: Gets a value indicating whether access to the <xref:System.Collections.ICollection> is synchronized (thread safe).
trans-unit.target: Henter en verdi som angir om tilgang til den <xref:System.Collections.ICollection>er synkronisert (tråden trygt).</xref:System.Collections.ICollection>

trans-unit.source: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref> if access to the <xref:System.Collections.ICollection> is synchronized (thread safe); otherwise, <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""></xref>.
trans-unit.target: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref>Hvis tilgang til den <xref:System.Collections.ICollection>er synkronisert (tråden trygt); ellers <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""> </xref>.</xref:System.Collections.ICollection>

trans-unit.source: Gets an object that can be used to synchronize access to the collection.
trans-unit.target: Henter et objekt som kan brukes til å synkronisere tilgang til samlingen.

trans-unit.source: An object that can be used to synchronize access to the collection.
trans-unit.target: Et objekt som kan brukes til å synkronisere tilgang til samlingen.

trans-unit.source: Gets a new enumerator for this collection.
trans-unit.target: Henter dataenumerator nye for denne samlingen.

trans-unit.target: En <xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator>som lister opp samlingen.</xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator>
